---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={"Totems Sacrés et Protection Antique | " + SITE_TITLE} description="Totems Sacrés et Protection Antique category page" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main class="category-page" style="width: 75%; max-width: none; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <header style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <h1>Totems Sacrés et Protection Antique</h1>
        </header>

        <section class="category-article" style="margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
            <p>La peur de l'invisible a engendré les plus beaux chefs-d'œuvre de la bijouterie. Cette dimension se concentre sur les talismans protecteurs, tels que l'Œil Bleu ou la Main de Fatma. Nous analysons ici le concept de "bijou bouclier". Le symbolisme de protection est universel, transcendant les frontières de la Méditerranée au Moyen-Orient. En décrivant la genèse de ces symboles, nous montrons comment le bijou sert de médiateur entre l'homme et le divin, ou entre le porteur et le "mauvais œil". Cette section explique la fonction apotropaïque du bijou : porter un symbole, c'est invoquer une présence protectrice et repousser les énergies négatives à travers des formes géométriques sacrées et des mythes millénaires.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="category-wp-content">
<figure class="wp-block-uagb-image__figure"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/media-images/posts/totems-et-protection-antique-illustration-1.webp" alt="Illustration for Totems Sacrés et Protection Antique" class="uag-image-1190" width="1200" height="350" title="Totems Sacrés et Protection Antique" role="img"></figure>
</section>



        



<section class="category-keywords" style="margin: 40px 0; padding: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.3rem;">Related Keywords</h3>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;">
        <span class="keyword-btn pending" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #888; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: not-allowed;">#oeil bleu grec signification</span>
        <span class="keyword-btn pending" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #888; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: not-allowed;">#main de fatma pendentif signification</span>
        <a href="/blog/scarabee-egyptien-joaillerie/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #9335B6); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#symbole scarabée égyptien bijoux</a>
        <span class="keyword-btn pending" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #888; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: not-allowed;">#protection mauvais oeil bijoux</span>
        <span class="keyword-btn pending" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #888; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: not-allowed;">#hamsa bijoux porte bonheur</span>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="category-faq-section" style="margin-top: 60px; padding: 40px 30px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #eaeaea;">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #222222; font-size: 2rem; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-content" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;">

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Signification de l'Œil Bleu ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Protection contre la jalousie d'autrui.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Main de Fatma origine ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Symbole de protection universel (Hamsa).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Scarabée sacré égyptien ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Symbole de renaissance et de cycle éternel.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Arbre de vie ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Connexion entre ciel, terre et racines.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Bijou cassé ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Signifie qu'il a absorbé un mal à votre place.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
